						"Huntail's presence went unnoticed by people for a long time because it lives at extreme depths in the sea. This Pokémon's eyes can see clearly even in the murky dark depths of the ocean.

name: Gorebyss
info:
Gorebyss is an unobtainable Water Pokémon which evolves from Clamperl. It is vulnerable to Grass and Electric moves. Gorebyss's strongest moveset is Water Gun & Water Pulse and it has a Max CP of 2,494.
					
						"Gorebyss lives in the southern seas at extreme depths. Its body is built to withstand the enormous pressure of water at incredible depths. Because of this, this Pokémon's body is unharmed by ordinary attacks.

name: Relicanth
info:
Relicanth is a regional Water & Rock Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Grass, Ground, Fighting and Electric moves. Relicanth's strongest moveset is Water Gun & Hydro Pump and it has a Max CP of 2,528. This Pokémon is only found in New Zealand and the surrounding islands.
					
						"Relicanth is a Pokémon species that existed for a hundred million years without ever changing its form. This ancient Pokémon feeds on microscopic organisms with its toothless mouth.

name: Luvdisc
info:
Luvdisc is a Water Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Grass and Electric moves. Luvdisc's strongest moveset is Water Gun & Water Pulse and it has a Max CP of 848.
					
						"Luvdisc live in shallow seas in the tropics. This heart-shaped Pokémon earned its name by swimming after loving couples it spotted in the ocean's waves.

name: Bagon
info:
Bagon is a Dragon Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fairy, Dragon and Ice moves. Bagon's strongest moveset is Bite & Flamethrower and it has a Max CP of 1,156. Bagon evolves into Shelgon.
					
						"Bagon has a dream of one day soaring in the sky. In doomed efforts to fly, this Pokémon hurls itself off cliffs. As a result of its dives, its head has grown tough and as hard as tempered steel.

name: Shelgon
info:
Shelgon is a Dragon Pokémon which evolves from Bagon. It is vulnerable to Fairy, Dragon and Ice moves. Shelgon's strongest moveset is Dragon Breath & Dragon Pulse and it has a Max CP of 2,031. Shelgon evolves into Salamence.
					
						"Inside Shelgon's armor-like shell, cells are in the midst of transformation to create an entirely new body. This Pokémon's shell is extremely heavy, making its movements sluggish.

name: Salamence
info:
Salamence is a Dragon & Flying Pokémon which evolves from Shelgon. It is vulnerable to Ice, Fairy, Dragon and Rock moves. Salamence's strongest moveset is Dragon Tail & Draco Meteor and it has a Max CP of 3,749.
					
						"Salamence came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerful desire triggered a sudden mutation in this Pokémon's cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings.

name: Beldum
info:
Beldum is a Steel & Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Dark, Ground and Ghost moves. Beldum's strongest moveset is Take Down & Struggle and it has a Max CP of 976. Beldum evolves into Metang.
					
						"Instead of blood, a powerful magnetic force courses throughout Beldum's body. This Pokémon communicates with others by sending controlled pulses of magnetism.

name: Metang
info:
Metang is a Steel & Psychic Pokémon which evolves from Beldum. It is vulnerable to Fire, Dark, Ground and Ghost moves. Metang's strongest moveset is Metal Claw & Psyshock and it has a Max CP of 1,721. Metang evolves into Metagross.
					
						"When two Beldum fuse together, Metang is formed. The brains of the Beldum are joined by a magnetic nervous system. By linking its brains magnetically, this Pokémon generates strong psychokinetic power.

name: Metagross
info:
Metagross is a Steel & Psychic Pokémon which evolves from Metang. It is vulnerable to Fire, Dark, Ground and Ghost moves. Metagross's strongest moveset is Bullet Punch & Meteor Mash and it has a Max CP of 3,791.
					
						"Metagross has four brains in total. Combined, the four brains can breeze through difficult calculations faster than a supercomputer. This Pokémon can float in the air by tucking in its four legs.

name: Regirock
info:
Regirock is an unobtainable legendary Rock Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Steel, Ground, Fighting, Water and Grass moves. Regirock's strongest moveset is Rock Throw & Stone Edge and it has a Max CP of 3,122.
					
						"Regirock was sealed away by people long ago. If this Pokémon's body is damaged in battle, it is said to seek out suitable rocks on its own to repair itself.

name: Regice
info:
Regice is a legendary Ice Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Fighting, Rock and Steel moves. Regice's strongest moveset is Frost Breath & Blizzard and it has a Max CP of 3,122.
					
						"Regice's body was made during an ice age. The deep-frozen body can't be melted, even by fire. This Pokémon controls frigid air of -328 degrees Fahrenheit.

name: Registeel
info:
Registeel is a legendary Steel Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Ground and Fighting moves. Registeel's strongest moveset is Metal Claw & Hyper Beam and it has a Max CP of 2,447.
					
						"Registeel has a body that is harder than any kind of metal. Its body is apparently hollow. No one has any idea what this Pokémon eats.

name: Latias
info:
Latias is a legendary Dragon & Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fairy, Ghost, Dark, Dragon, Ice and Bug moves. Latias's strongest moveset is Dragon Breath & Outrage and it has a Max CP of 3,510.
					
						"Latias is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this Pokémon ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.

name: Latios
info:
Latios is a legendary Dragon & Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fairy, Ghost, Dark, Dragon, Ice and Bug moves. Latios's strongest moveset is Dragon Breath & Dragon Claw and it has a Max CP of 3,812.
					
						"Latios has the ability to make others see an image of what it has seen or imagines in its head. This Pokémon is intelligent and understands human speech.

name: Kyogre
info:
Kyogre is a legendary Water Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Grass and Electric moves. Kyogre's strongest moveset is Waterfall & Hydro Pump and it has a Max CP of 4,115.
					
						"Through Primal Reversion and with nature's full power, it will take back its true form. It can summon storms that cause the sea levels to rise.

name: Groudon
info:
Groudon is a legendary Ground Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Grass, Ice and Water moves. Groudon's strongest moveset is Dragon Tail & Solar Beam and it has a Max CP of 4,115.
					
						"Groudon is said to be the personification of the land itself. Legends tell of its many clashes against Kyogre, as each sought to gain the power of nature.

name: Rayquaza
info:
Rayquaza is a legendary Dragon & Flying Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Ice, Fairy, Dragon and Rock moves. Rayquaza's strongest moveset is Dragon Tail & Outrage and it has a Max CP of 3,835.
					
						"Rayquaza is said to have lived for hundreds of millions of years. Legends remain of how it put to rest the clash between Kyogre and Groudon.

name: Jirachi
info:
Jirachi is an unobtainable mythical Steel & Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Dark, Ground and Ghost moves. Jirachi's strongest moveset is Confusion & Doom Desire and it has a Max CP of 3,265.
					
						"A legend states that Jirachi will make true any wish that is written on notes attached to its head when it awakens. If this Pokémon senses danger, it will fight without awakening.

name: Deoxys
info:
Deoxys (Speed) is a mythical Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Bug, Dark and Ghost moves. Deoxys's strongest moveset is Zen Headbutt & Thunderbolt and it has a Max CP of 2,879.
					
						"The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in Deoxys. The crystalline organ on this Pokémon's chest appears to be its brain.

name: Deoxys
info:
Deoxys (Normal) is a mythical Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Bug, Dark and Ghost moves. Deoxys's strongest moveset is Zen Headbutt & Hyper Beam and it has a Max CP of 3,160.
					
						"The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in Deoxys. The crystalline organ on this Pokémon's chest appears to be its brain.

name: Deoxys
info:
Deoxys (Attack) is a mythical Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Bug, Dark and Ghost moves. Deoxys's strongest moveset is Zen Headbutt & Zap Cannon and it has a Max CP of 2,580.
					
						"The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in Deoxys. The crystalline organ on this Pokémon's chest appears to be its brain.

name: Deoxys
info:
Deoxys (Defense) is a mythical Psychic Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Bug, Dark and Ghost moves. Deoxys's strongest moveset is Counter & Thunderbolt and it has a Max CP of 2,274.
					
						"The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in Deoxys. The crystalline organ on this Pokémon's chest appears to be its brain.

name: Turtwig
info:
Turtwig is a Grass Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Bug and Ice moves. Turtwig's strongest moveset is Razor Leaf & Seed Bomb and it has a Max CP of 1,187. Turtwig evolves into Grotle.
					
						"It undertakes photosynthesis with its body, making oxygen. The leaf on its head wilts if it is thirsty.

name: Grotle
info:
Grotle is a Grass Pokémon which evolves from Turtwig. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Bug and Ice moves. Grotle's strongest moveset is Razor Leaf & Solar Beam and it has a Max CP of 1,890. Grotle evolves into Torterra.
					
						"It knows where pure water wells up. It carries fellow Pokémon there on its back.

name: Torterra
info:
Torterra is a Grass & Ground Pokémon which evolves from Grotle. It is vulnerable to Ice, Fire, Flying and Bug moves. Torterra's strongest moveset is Razor Leaf & Solar Beam and it has a Max CP of 2,934.
					
						"Small Pokémon occasionally gather on its unmoving back to begin building their nests.

name: Chimchar
info:
Chimchar is a Fire Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Ground, Rock and Water moves. Chimchar's strongest moveset is Ember & Flamethrower and it has a Max CP of 957. Chimchar evolves into Monferno.
					
						"The gas made in its belly burns from its rear end. The fire burns weakly when it feels sick.

name: Monferno
info:
Monferno is a Fire & Fighting Pokémon which evolves from Chimchar. It is vulnerable to Flying, Ground, Psychic and Water moves. Monferno's strongest moveset is Ember & Flamethrower and it has a Max CP of 1,574. Monferno evolves into Infernape.
					
						"It uses ceilings and walls to launch aerial attacks. Its fiery tail is but one weapon.

name: Infernape
info:
Infernape is a Fire & Fighting Pokémon which evolves from Monferno. It is vulnerable to Flying, Ground, Psychic and Water moves. Infernape's strongest moveset is Fire Spin & Flamethrower and it has a Max CP of 2,683.
					
						"It tosses its enemies around with agility. It uses all its limbs to fight in its own unique style.

name: Piplup
info:
Piplup is a Water Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Grass and Electric moves. Piplup's strongest moveset is Bubble & Bubble Beam and it has a Max CP of 1,075. Piplup evolves into Prinplup.
					
						"Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.

name: Prinplup
info:
Prinplup is a Water Pokémon which evolves from Piplup. It is vulnerable to Grass and Electric moves. Prinplup's strongest moveset is Bubble & Hydro Pump and it has a Max CP of 1,701. Prinplup evolves into Empoleon.
					
						"It lives a solitary life. Its wings deliver wicked blows that can snap even the thickest of trees.

name: Empoleon
info:
Empoleon is a Water & Steel Pokémon which evolves from Prinplup. It is vulnerable to Fighting, Ground and Electric moves. Empoleon's strongest moveset is Metal Claw & Hydro Pump and it has a Max CP of 2,900.
					
						"The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.

name: Starly
info:
Starly is a Normal & Flying Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Ice, Rock and Electric moves. Starly's strongest moveset is Quick Attack & Brave Bird and it has a Max CP of 719. Starly evolves into Staravia.
					
						"They flock around mountains and fields, chasing after bug Pokémon. Their singing is noisy and annoying.

name: Staravia
info:
Staravia is a Normal & Flying Pokémon which evolves from Starly. It is vulnerable to Ice, Rock and Electric moves. Staravia's strongest moveset is Quick Attack & Brave Bird and it has a Max CP of 1,299. Staravia evolves into Staraptor.
					
						"It lives in forests and fields. Squabbles over territory occur when flocks collide.

name: Staraptor
info:
Staraptor is a Normal & Flying Pokémon which evolves from Staravia. It is vulnerable to Ice, Rock and Electric moves. Staraptor's strongest moveset is Quick Attack & Brave Bird and it has a Max CP of 2,825.
					
						"When Staravia evolve into Staraptor, they leave the flock to live alone. They have sturdy wings.

name: Bidoof
info:
Bidoof is a Normal Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fighting moves. Bidoof's strongest moveset is Tackle & Hyper Fang and it has a Max CP of 721. Bidoof evolves into Bibarel.
					
						"It constantly gnaws on logs and rocks to whittle down its front teeth. It nests alongside water.

name: Bibarel
info:
Bibarel is a Normal & Water Pokémon which evolves from Bidoof. It is vulnerable to Fighting, Electric and Grass moves. Bibarel's strongest moveset is Water Gun & Hyper Beam and it has a Max CP of 1,823.
					
						"It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.

name: Kricketot
info:
Kricketot is a Bug Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying and Rock moves. Kricketot's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Struggle and it has a Max CP of 401. Kricketot evolves into Kricketune.
					
						"When its antennae hit each other, it sounds like the music of a xylophone.

name: Kricketune
info:
Kricketune is a Bug Pokémon which evolves from Kricketot. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying and Rock moves. Kricketune's strongest moveset is Fury Cutter & Bug Buzz and it has a Max CP of 1,653.
					
						"It signals its emotions with its melodies. Scientists are studying these melodic patterns.

name: Shinx
info:
Shinx is an Electric Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Ground moves. Shinx's strongest moveset is Spark & Thunderbolt and it has a Max CP of 876. Shinx evolves into Luxio.
					
						"All of its fur dazzles if danger is sensed. It flees while the foe is momentarily blinded.

name: Luxio
info:
Luxio is an Electric Pokémon which evolves from Shinx. It is vulnerable to Ground moves. Luxio's strongest moveset is Spark & Wild Charge and it has a Max CP of 1,486. Luxio evolves into Luxray.
					
						"Strong electricity courses through the tips of its sharp claws. A light scratch causes fainting in foes.

name: Luxray
info:
Luxray is an Electric Pokémon which evolves from Luxio. It is vulnerable to Ground moves. Luxray's strongest moveset is Spark & Wild Charge and it has a Max CP of 2,888.
					
						"Luxray's ability to see through objects comes in handy when it's scouting for danger.

name: Budew
info:
Budew is a Grass & Poison Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice and Psychic moves. Budew's strongest moveset is Razor Leaf & Grass Knot and it has a Max CP of 856. Budew evolves into Roselia.
					
						"Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: Roserade
info:
Roserade is a Grass & Poison Pokémon which evolves from Roselia. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice and Psychic moves. Roserade's strongest moveset is Poison Jab & Solar Beam and it has a Max CP of 2,971.
					
						"With the movements of a dancer, it strikes with whips that are densely lined with poison thorns.

name: Cranidos
info:
Cranidos is a Rock Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Steel, Ground, Fighting, Water and Grass moves. Cranidos's strongest moveset is Zen Headbutt & Ancient Power and it has a Max CP of 1,820. Cranidos evolves into Rampardos.
					
						"Its hard skull is its distinguishing feature. It snapped trees by headbutting them, and then it fed on their ripe berries.

name: Rampardos
info:
Rampardos is a Rock Pokémon which evolves from Cranidos. It is vulnerable to Steel, Ground, Fighting, Water and Grass moves. Rampardos's strongest moveset is Smack Down & Rock Slide and it has a Max CP of 3,298.
					
						"This ancient Pokémon used headbutts skillfully. Its brain was really small, so some theories suggest that its stupidity led to its extinction.

name: Shieldon
info:
Shieldon is a Rock & Steel Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Ground, Fighting and Water moves. Shieldon's strongest moveset is Iron Tail & Heavy Slam and it has a Max CP of 890. Shieldon evolves into Bastiodon.
					
						"Although its fossils can be found in layers of primeval rock, nothing but its face has ever been discovered.

name: Bastiodon
info:
Bastiodon is a Rock & Steel Pokémon which evolves from Shieldon. It is vulnerable to Ground, Fighting and Water moves. Bastiodon's strongest moveset is Iron Tail & Stone Edge and it has a Max CP of 1,539.
					
						"This Pokémon is from roughly 100 million years ago. Its terrifyingly tough face is harder than steel.

name: Burmy
info:
Burmy (Trash) is a Bug Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying and Rock moves. Burmy's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Struggle and it has a Max CP of 488. Burmy evolves into Wormadam, Mothim.
					
						"If its cloak is broken in battle, it quickly remakes the cloak with materials nearby.

name: Burmy
info:
Burmy (Sandy) is a Bug Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying and Rock moves. Burmy's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Struggle and it has a Max CP of 488. Burmy evolves into Wormadam, Mothim.
					
						"If its cloak is broken in battle, it quickly remakes the cloak with materials nearby.

name: Burmy
info:
Burmy (Plant) is a Bug Pokémon. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying and Rock moves. Burmy's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Struggle and it has a Max CP of 488. Burmy evolves into Wormadam, Mothim.
					
						"If its cloak is broken in battle, it quickly remakes the cloak with materials nearby.

name: Wormadam
info:
Wormadam (Sandy) is a Bug & Ground Pokémon which evolves from Burmy. It is vulnerable to Fire, Water, Flying and Ice moves. Wormadam's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Bug Buzz and it has a Max CP of 1,773.
					
						"When Burmy evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon's body. The cloak is never shed.

name: Wormadam
info:
Wormadam (Plant) is a Bug & Grass Pokémon which evolves from Burmy. It is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Rock, Bug and Ice moves. Wormadam's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Bug Buzz and it has a Max CP of 1,773.
					
						"When Burmy evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon's body. The cloak is never shed.

name: Wormadam
info:
Wormadam (Trash) is a Bug & Steel Pokémon which evolves from Burmy. It is vulnerable to Fire moves. Wormadam's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Bug Buzz and it has a Max CP of 1,593.
					
						"When Burmy evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon's body. The cloak is never shed.

name: Mothim
info:
Mothim is a Bug & Flying Pokémon which evolves from Burmy. It is vulnerable to Rock, Fire, Flying, Ice and Electric moves. Mothim's strongest moveset is Bug Bite & Bug Buzz and it has a Max CP of 1,815.
					
						"It flutters around at night and steals honey from the Combee hive.

info:

						"It melts particles of iron and other metals found in the subsoil, so it can absorb them into its body of molten steel.

name: Melmetal
info:
